        <Parent_String>ceramic tile by technique [300010722], ceramic tile [300010678], ceramic by product [300157780], ceramic and ceramic by product [300151340], clay by product [300010462], clay [300010439], inorganic material [300010360], materials by composition [300212963], materials (substances) [300010358], Materials (hierarchy name) [300010357], Materials Facet [300264091]</Parent_String>
